quran[29]{c,v,t}:
  27,27,"Solomon kaa sε: “Yε’bεhwε sε, deε woreka no yε nokorε anaasε woka nkontompofoͻ no ho"
  27,28,"Fa menwoma yi kͻ na fa kͻma wͻn, na afei dane woho fri wͻn ho (bra), na yεnhwε (mmuaeε) a wͻ’de bεba“"
  27,29,"(Ɔhemaa no) kaa sε: ”Nhemfo, nokorε sε yεde animuonyam nwoma bi aberε me"
  27,30,"Nokorε sε efri Solomon hͻ, na nokorε sε (me hyj asej wc) Nyankopͻn din mu, Ahummͻborͻ Hene, Ɔdεεfoͻ Hene. (Bismi Laahir-Rah’maanir-Rahiim)"
  27,31,"(Emu nsεm ne sε): “Monhwε na moanyε ahomasoͻ antia me, na mmom momra mehͻ sε Muslimifoͻ wͻ ahobraseε mu"
  27,32,"(Ɔhemaa no) kaa sε: Nhemfo, mo mame adwen wͻ m’asεm yi ho. Menfa adwen wͻ asεm bi ho gyesε moka me ho (ne me dwene ho) ansa"
  27,33,"(Nhemfo no) kaa sε: “Yεn ho yε den paa, na yεwͻ ͻkoo mu nso ahoͻden papaapa; na wohɔ na tumi no wͻ, enti hwε deε wobεhyε sε yεnyε”"
  27,34,"(Ɔhemaa no) kaa sε: “Nokorε sε, (Solomon) nhemfo no, sε wͻ’wura kuro bi mu a wͻ’sεe no pasaa, na wͻ’brε kuro no mu atitiriwfoͻ ne adehyeε no ase korakora. Na saa na wͻ’yε”"
  27,35,Nokorԑ sԑ mede akyεdeε bԑsoma ama yεde akͻma wͻn na yahwε (mmuaε) a asomafoͻ no bεsan de aba “
  27,36,"Ɛberε a (asomafoͻ no) baa Solomon hͻ no, ͻkaa sε: “Ahonya deε na mode rema no abu me soͻ? Deε Nyankopͻn de ama me no kyεn deε Ɔde ama mo. Daabi, mona moanigye moakyεdeε no ho “"
  27,37,"(Solomon ka kyerεε Ɔhemaa no bͻfo panin no sε): “San wakyi kͻ wͻn hͻ, na yεde dͻm a wͻ’nntumi nyina ano bεba wͻn so, na y’abetu wͻn mu atitiriwfoͻ no afri kuro no mu, na y’agu wͻn anim ase “"
  27,38,"(Solomon) kaa sε: ”Mpanimfoͻ, momu hwan na ͻde n’ahennwa no bεbrε me ansa na wͻ’de ahobraseε aba me hᴐ?”"
  27,39,"Jinn no mu ͻhodenfoͻ (Ifriit) kaa sε: “Mede bεbrε wo ansa na w’asͻre afri faako a woteε yi. Nokorε sε mewͻ ahoͻden afei medi nokorε wͻ adwuma a εte saa no ho"
  27,40,"Nea ͻwͻ Nyamesεm Nwoma no ho nimdeε no kaa sε: “Mede bεbrε wo ntεmso (tesε obi abͻ na’ani ateε). Ԑberε a Solomon hunuu sε (Ɔhemaa no ahennwa) no si n’anim no, ͻkaa sε: “Woi yε adom a efri me Wura Nyankopͻn hͻ sεdeε Ɔde bεsͻ me ahwε sε meyi (N’ayε) anaa meyi (no) boniayε. Obi a obeyi (Nyankopͻn) ayε no, oyi ayε dema ͻno ara neho, na obia obeyi boniayε no nso nokorε sε, me Wura Nyankopͻn deε W’anya Neho, Ɔne Adom ne Animuonyam Hene"
  27,41,"(Solomon) kaa sε: “Monyε nsakraeε wͻ n’ahennwa no ho ma no na yεnhwε sε w’anya kwankyerε, anaasε ͻka wͻn a wͻ’nnyaa kwan kyerε no ho.“"
  27,42,"Ɛberε a ͻbaeε no yεkakyerεε no sε: “Enti w’ahennwa no sei na εteε?” Ɔkaa sε: “Ɛbεka sε εyε noa “.(Solomon kaa sε): Y’adi kan anya ɛho nimdeε ansa na ͻreba. Na yε’deε yε’yε Muslimifoͻ dada”"
  27,43,Deε na (Ɔhemaa Bilqiis) fri Nyankopͻn akyi somoeε no sii no (Nyamesom ho) kwan efrisε na ͻka amanfoͻ boniyεfoͻ no ho
  27,44,"Yε’ka kyerεε (Ɔhemaa) no sε: “Wura ahemfie kεseε no mu”. Ɛberε a ohunuuiε no n’adwen yεε no sε εyε asu tadeε bi, enti (ͻpagya n’ataadeε) yii nenan ho. Solomon kaa sε: “Ɛyε ahemfie a yεde nhwehwε na ayε no kokwakokwa“. Ɔhemmaa Bilqiis kaa sε: ”Me Wura Nyankopͻn, nokorε sε m’ayε bͻne atia me ho, na m’aka Solomon ho abrε me ho ase (sε Muslim) de ama Abͻdeε nyinaa Wura no"
  27,45,"Nokorε nso sε Yε’somaa Samuudfoͻ nua Soalhu maa no kͻͻ wͻn hͻ sε (ͻnkͻka nkyerε wͻn) sε: “Monsom mo Wura Nyankopͻn“. Na hwε, wͻ’bεyεε akuo mmienu a wͻ’reko tia wͻn ho"
  27,46,"(Soalhu) kaa sε: ”Menkorͻfoͻ, adεn nti na morepere moho de bͻne adi papa anim kan? Adεn nti na monsrε Nyankopͻn hͻ bͻnefakyε sεdeε ebia yεbehu mo mmͻbͻ?”"
  27,47,"Wͻ’kaa sε: “Wone wͻn a wͻ’ka wo ho no yε mmusuo ma yεn“. Soalhu kaa sε: ”Mo mmusuo no fri Nyankopͻn hͻ; daabi, moyε nnipa a mowͻ nsͻhwε mu “"
  27,48,Na mmarima nkron bi wͻ kuro no mu a wͻ’di nsεmmͻne wͻ asaase no so a wͻ’nnyε ntotoeε pa
  27,49,"Wͻ’kaa sε: “Monfa Nyankopͻn nni nse nkyerε moho-moho sε, yεbεkͻ akͻto ahyε Soalhu ne n’abusuafoͻ so anadwo, na yaka akyerε nenkorͻfoͻ sε: “Yennim ͻne n’abusuafoͻ wuo no ho hwee, na nokorε na yεreka no“"
  27,50,"Enti wͻ’bͻͻ pͻ paa, na Yεn nso Yε’bͻͻ pͻ paa wͻ aberε a na wͻ’nnim"
  27,51,"Enti hwε sεdeε wͻn pͻbͻͻ no aweε si wieε! Nokorε, Yε’sεee wͻ’ne wͻn nkorͻfoͻ no nyinaa pasaa"
  27,52,"Sεdeε wͻn afie si yͻeε no-, adane amanfoo, εnam wͻn bͻne nti. Nokorε sε nsεnkyerεnee wͻ woi mu dema amanfoͻ a wͻnim"
  27,53,Yε’gyee wͻn a wͻ’gye diiε no a na wͻ’suro Nyame no nkwa
  27,54,"Lut nso, εberε a ͻka kyerεε nenkorͻfoͻ no sε: “Adεn, mobu bra bͻne wͻ aberε a moani tua"
  27,55,"Mofri mmaa no akyi de akͻnnͻ kͻ mmarima so? Daabi, moyε amanfoͻ bi a moadwen awuo"